                <h1>Customize Your Safari Background: A Quick Guide</h1>
                <p>To change your Safari background, open the Safari app on your iPhone or iPad. Navigate to the "Settings" and select "Safari." Scroll to "Background Image" and choose your desired image from your photos or select one of the default options. Tap "Done" to save your changes and enjoy a personalized browsing experience!</p>
